    <who name="maarten meijer">mjmeijer</who>
    <bug_when>2011-02-23 10:06:40 -0500</bug_when>
    <thetext>SWTDesigner is now free as part of Google WindowBuilder. Its is a good tool to design RepositoryQueryWizard and other pages.
The Design view cannot be used because of code in org.eclipse.mylyn.tasks.ui.wizards.AbstractRepositoryQueryPage.AbstractRepositoryQueryPage(String, TaskRepository, IRepositoryQuery)

The solution is described here:
http://ekkescorner.wordpress.com/2009/07/07/galileo-enter-the-twilight-zone-between-target-platform-runtime-and-ide-development/

I attach a patch with the changes but this will not be enough as other code may also be affected.</thetext>
  </long_desc><long_desc isprivate="0" >
